{"tid":1681772,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【林俊傑針頭出售】","createTime":"2019-10-29T15:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T17:26:17.000Z","uid":307619,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"501a0272ce8b05b674547b3502ef5979982b18f2","tid":1681772,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"【林俊傑針頭出售事件 11人停職 】 <br />\n<br />\n新加坡歌手林俊傑上星期六在江蘇省鎮江市舉行演唱會後，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因感冒到鎮江第一人民醫院打吊針，之後有聲稱林俊傑使用過的針頭和注射液包裝袋在網上出售。<br />\n<br />\n醫院的多名工作人員又被揭發，輪流在林俊傑躺過的病床上拍照。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當局經調查後，將醫院11名工作人員停職。<br />\n<br />\n#粉絲經濟有無道德底線<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hg4UhJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhg4UhJA.jpg&h=ebc78ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdSVMCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdSVMCN.jpg&h=492d44c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明日香港！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6621bfb7eb06a03ddef53b0bf089a4eab941c0ae","tid":1681772,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLXe8W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLXe8W.jpg&h=d3761788&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1943c0b1b630ce2487a8c58dcf93ec9a83c80014","tid":1681772,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:59:18.000Z","msg":"戀上你的床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7199221eda1c3b89d7926116a49c4b95bd69f7","tid":1681772,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e7c8b7322115b66cf233a8d4d9fd09223498d9e","tid":1681772,"uid":111670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:04:51.0